Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:17.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\fad(100,100)}那远方闪耀的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:23.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\fad(100,100)}有着寻求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:25.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.333\fad(100,100)}相信着
